 12 the war and magician will be on par.<br>
Actually a warrior untwinked can solo his way up to level 30. I don't say that this will be quick, but my girlfriend passed a logn time in overthere. Now she is level 50 and is still trying to solo some times, but it is really hard at this level if you are not twinked, mobs hurt a lot. Soloing a warrior up to 20 is easy believe me.<br>
